e-commerce
=====

1. for installation error when installing Nikigori:
   $ brew install libxml2
   $ bundle config build.nokogiri "--use-system-libraries --with-xml2-include=/usr/local/opt/libxml2/include/libxml2"
   $ bundle install
   [Reference]: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/23668684/failed-to-build-gem-native-extension-when-i-run-bundle-install